ingredients: ALFREDO SAUCE: WATER, SOYBEAN OIL, ROMANO CHEESE (SHEEP'S MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES, CALCIUM PROPIONATE), CREAM, PARMESAN CHEESE (COW'S MILK, CHEESE CULTURE, SALT, ENZYMES, CALCIUM PROPIONATE), CONTAINS LESS THAN 2% OF MODIFIED FOOD STARCH, SALT, BUTTER FLAVORING (WHEY SOLIDS, ENZYME-MODIFIED BUTTER [BUTTER, BUTTERMILK POWDER, ENZYMES], MALTODEXTRIN, SALT, DEHYDRATED BUTTER [BUTTER, BUTTERMILK POWDER], GUAR GUM, ANNATTO AND TURMERIC [FOR COLOR]), SWEET WHEY, SPICES, CITRIC ACID, DEHYDRATED GARLIC, DISODIUM INOSINATE AND DISODIUM GUANYLATE. FETTUCINE PASTA: ENRICHED SEMOLINA FLOUR (SEMOLINA, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, EGGS. GRILLED CHICKEN BREAST STRIPS: BONELESS, SKINLESS, CHICKEN BREAST WITH RIB MEAT, CONTAINS UP TO 15% SOLUTION OF WATER, SALT, SODIUM PHOSPHATE, LESS THAN 2% SOY BEAN OIL AS A PROCESSING AID. CHEESE BLEND: PARMESAN CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK RENNET AND SALT), ROMANO CHEESE (PASTEURIZED MILK, RENNET, AND SALT).
